00:18:02.520 --> 00:18:03.565 align:middle line:90%
You won't need experts.

00:18:03.565 --> 00:18:04.440 align:middle line:90%
You won't need gurus.

00:18:04.440 --> 00:18:05.580 align:middle line:90%
