00:19:05.440 --> 00:19:06.240 align:middle line:90%
It's terrifying.

00:19:06.240 --> 00:19:07.440 align:middle line:90%
>> But we do need teachers.

00:19:07.440 --> 00:19:10.420 align:middle line:84%
I mean, you said, we won't need
gurus, but we need teachers.

00:19:10.420 --> 00:19:11.220 align:middle line:90%
Don't we?

00:19:11.220 --> 00:19:12.570 align:middle line:90%
Aren't you a teacher?

00:19:12.570 --> 00:19:14.250 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes, I hope I am.

00:19:14.250 --> 00:19:16.770 align:middle line:84%
But what I hope I'm
teaching is how to learn.

00:19:16.770 --> 00:19:20.610 align:middle line:84%
I think we need teachers who
know that they are seekers, who

00:19:20.610 --> 00:19:24.390 align:middle line:84%
know that they are learners,
who do not want power, who want

00:19:24.390 --> 00:19:27.420 align:middle line:84%
the authority not of
power but of love,

00:19:27.420 --> 00:19:31.735 align:middle line:84%
and who are there to teach from
their own experience what they

00:19:31.735 --> 00:19:36.140 align:middle line:84%
are learning, who don't teach
from a omnipotent omniscient

00:19:36.140 --> 00:19:39.720 align:middle line:84%
position, because no one,
no one, including Jesus

00:19:39.720 --> 00:19:42.900 align:middle line:84%
and including Rumi and
including Ramakrishnan

00:19:42.900 --> 00:19:45.930 align:middle line:84%
would ever, ever claim to
know everything if they'd seen

00:19:45.930 --> 00:19:47.490 align:middle line:90%
a glimpse of the glory of God.

00:19:47.490 --> 00:19:48.870 align:middle line:90%
It is outrageous.

00:19:48.870 --> 00:19:51.450 align:middle line:84%
Those gurus and priests who
claimed to know everything

00:19:51.450 --> 00:19:54.630 align:middle line:84%
are simply indulging in a
form of monstrous manipulation

00:19:54.630 --> 00:19:56.997 align:middle line:90%
that is absolutely impossible.

00:19:56.997 --> 00:19:59.580 align:middle line:84%
Let me tell you a lovely story
of Rumi at the end of his life.

00:19:59.580 --> 00:20:01.578 align:middle line:84%
Rumi was the great
King of mystics

00:20:01.578 --> 00:20:03.870 align:middle line:84%
who was revered even in his
own time as a great mystic.

00:20:03.870 --> 00:20:04.670 align:middle line:90%
>> Brilliant.

00:20:04.670 --> 00:20:07.210 align:middle line:84%
>> The most wonderful mystic
perhaps the world has ever

00:20:07.210 --> 00:20:08.010 align:middle line:90%
seen.

00:20:08.010 --> 00:20:11.100 align:middle line:84%
A young man had heard about
him and was terribly thrilled

00:20:11.100 --> 00:20:13.580 align:middle line:84%
and was projecting
endlessly onto Rumi

00:20:13.580 --> 00:20:15.720 align:middle line:84%
how glorious he must
be, came all the way

00:20:15.720 --> 00:20:16.890 align:middle line:90%
from Constantinople.

00:20:16.890 --> 00:20:19.890 align:middle line:84%
He met Rumi walking
outside Konya.

00:20:19.890 --> 00:20:20.820 align:middle line:90%
He bowed to Rumi.

00:20:20.820 --> 00:20:21.960 align:middle line:90%
Rumi bowed to him.

00:20:21.960 --> 00:20:23.010 align:middle line:90%
He bowed again to Rumi.

00:20:23.010 --> 00:20:24.330 align:middle line:90%
Rumi bowed to him.

00:20:24.330 --> 00:20:27.635 align:middle line:84%
Rumi about 32 times to the
man until the man got it.

00:20:27.635 --> 00:20:29.010 align:middle line:84%
And the man cried
out, oh my god,

00:20:29.010 --> 00:20:31.203 align:middle line:84%
why do you treat
me like this, you

00:20:31.203 --> 00:20:32.370 align:middle line:90%
who are the King of mystics?

00:20:32.370 --> 00:20:34.740 align:middle line:84%
And Rumi said to
him, if I did not

00:20:34.740 --> 00:20:37.260 align:middle line:84%
show you my misery
and my nothingness

00:20:37.260 --> 00:20:39.960 align:middle line:90%
before God, what use would I be?

00:20:39.960 --> 00:20:45.450 align:middle line:84%
So what Rumi is teaching
is the very humility

00:20:45.450 --> 00:20:48.630 align:middle line:84%
through which Rumi has learned
everything that he is learning.

00:20:48.630 --> 00:20:49.930 align:middle line:90%
That is what we need.

00:20:49.930 --> 00:20:52.560 align:middle line:84%
We don't need teachers in
the conventional sense.

00:20:52.560 --> 00:20:54.720 align:middle line:84%
We need mirrors of
divine love in which

00:20:54.720 --> 00:20:57.270 align:middle line:90%
we can see our own real face.

00:20:57.270 --> 00:21:00.210 align:middle line:84%
We need people who can
teach us how to learn.

00:21:00.210 --> 00:21:04.320 align:middle line:84%
We need people who have really
been humbled and radically

00:21:04.320 --> 00:21:08.340 align:middle line:84%
humbled by direct divine
experience which would totally

00:21:08.340 --> 00:21:10.680 align:middle line:84%
stop them being
teachers of any kind

00:21:10.680 --> 00:21:15.840 align:middle line:84%
and make them lovers and sharers
and invite us to a great feast.

00:21:15.840 --> 00:21:18.480 align:middle line:84%
>> One of the things you spoke
of a little bit earlier was

00:21:18.480 --> 00:21:21.270 align:middle line:84%
the importance of
being of service.

00:21:21.270 --> 00:21:23.850 align:middle line:84%
How do people mobilize
to begin that?

00:21:23.850 --> 00:21:26.670 align:middle line:84%
>> There are five forms of
service and it's very simple

00:21:26.670 --> 00:21:27.990 align:middle line:90%
when you get it.

00:21:27.990 --> 00:21:31.140 align:middle line:84%
First, you serve the divine
by loving the divine.

00:21:31.140 --> 00:21:32.580 align:middle line:84%
And then you serve
the part of you

00:21:32.580 --> 00:21:35.068 align:middle line:84%
that is always in
connection with the divine

00:21:35.068 --> 00:21:37.110 align:middle line:84%
and that is by praying
and meditating and keeping

00:21:37.110 --> 00:21:38.970 align:middle line:90%
that connection alive.

00:21:38.970 --> 00:21:42.090 align:middle line:84%
Then you serve the people
in your life, your friends,

00:21:42.090 --> 00:21:44.870 align:middle line:84%
your family, your sentient
beings, your pets.

00:21:44.870 --> 00:21:47.120 align:middle line:84%
And you serve them,
if you possibly can,

00:21:47.120 --> 00:21:49.460 align:middle line:84%
as representatives
of the divine.

00:21:49.460 --> 00:21:52.490 align:middle line:84%
And then, you serve
your community,

00:21:52.490 --> 00:21:56.570 align:middle line:84%
because you serve your community
by really taking care of what

00:21:56.570 --> 00:21:58.290 align:middle line:90%
is going on in your community.

00:21:58.290 --> 00:22:00.050 align:middle line:84%
How are the poor
people being treated?

00:22:00.050 --> 00:22:01.550 align:middle line:90%
What are the hospitals like?

00:22:01.550 --> 00:22:03.360 align:middle line:84%
Are the bus shelters
really helpful?

00:22:03.360 --> 00:22:04.160 align:middle line:90%
You look around.

00:22:04.160 --> 00:22:05.150 align:middle line:90%
You get informed.

00:22:05.150 --> 00:22:08.840 align:middle line:84%
And then of course, you serve
the whole global community

00:22:08.840 --> 00:22:11.000 align:middle line:84%
by really staying
in touch, by really

00:22:11.000 --> 00:22:14.990 align:middle line:84%
being aware of what is happening
in this environmental horror we

00:22:14.990 --> 00:22:18.170 align:middle line:84%
find ourselves in, in what's
happening in global poverty.

00:22:18.170 --> 00:22:21.110 align:middle line:84%
All of these forms of
service are different facets

00:22:21.110 --> 00:22:23.550 align:middle line:90%
of one diamond of divine love.

00:22:23.550 --> 00:22:28.130 align:middle line:84%
And if you really love God and
the world and other people,

00:22:28.130 --> 00:22:30.890 align:middle line:84%
it will breed in you
an overwhelming passion

00:22:30.890 --> 00:22:35.510 align:middle line:84%
to do good, to do real good,
to make justice happen.

00:22:35.510 --> 00:22:37.640 align:middle line:84%
And that will inevitably
express itself

00:22:37.640 --> 00:22:39.320 align:middle line:84%
on all of these
different levels,

00:22:39.320 --> 00:22:41.370 align:middle line:84%
in all of these
five different ways.

00:22:41.370 --> 00:22:43.520 align:middle line:84%
And when you fuse
them together, you

00:22:43.520 --> 00:22:47.270 align:middle line:84%
become someone who is
world-centered, god-centered,

00:22:47.270 --> 00:22:49.430 align:middle line:90%
and not self-centered.

00:22:49.430 --> 00:22:50.930 align:middle line:84%
And that's a very
difficult process.

00:22:50.930 --> 00:22:52.050 align:middle line:90%
It's a slow process.

00:22:52.050 --> 00:22:53.540 align:middle line:90%
It doesn't come instantly.

00:22:53.540 --> 00:22:55.250 align:middle line:84%
But the rewards
are extraordinary,

00:22:55.250 --> 00:22:58.370 align:middle line:84%
because then you really are
serving the transformation

00:22:58.370 --> 00:23:00.050 align:middle line:84%
that love is trying
to bring about.

00:23:00.050 --> 00:23:03.450 align:middle line:84%
>> You know, Mr.
Harvey, you are divine.

00:23:03.450 --> 00:23:04.250 align:middle line:90%
>> So are you.

00:23:04.250 --> 00:23:06.980 align:middle line:84%
And so is everyone else
watching this program.

00:23:06.980 --> 00:23:10.330 align:middle line:84%
We are all divine
children of the divine.

00:23:10.330 --> 00:23:13.400 align:middle line:84%
And no one is more
special than anyone else.

00:23:13.400 --> 00:23:15.410 align:middle line:90%
Some have seen it.

00:23:15.410 --> 00:23:17.360 align:middle line:90%
Others will see it.

00:23:17.360 --> 00:23:18.680 align:middle line:90%
It is available.

00:23:18.680 --> 00:23:19.490 align:middle line:90%
Claim it.

00:23:19.490 --> 00:23:20.290 align:middle line:90%
Live it.

00:23:20.290 --> 00:23:21.350 align:middle line:90%
Serve it.

00:23:21.350 --> 00:23:23.910 align:middle line:84%
And all things will come
amazingly clear to you.

00:23:23.910 --> 00:23:26.610 align:middle line:90%


